laboratory_examinations.findings: Ms. A was treated with 80-100 mg/day of fluoxetine, which controlled her obsessions well; however, no medication had a substantial effect on her urges to binge and purge.
laboratory_examinations.changes_over_time: Fluoxetine dosage maintained at 100 mg/day during the last phase, helping to prevent major fluctuations in mood and control obsessional thoughts.
